self.name: maskCoords
self.description: Position on a photo where a mask should be placed
self.descriptionExcerpt: Position on a photo where a mask should be placed

arguments.name: n
arguments.description: Part of the face, relative to which the mask should be placed

arguments.name: x
arguments.description: Shift by X-axis measured in widths of the mask scaled to the face size, from left to right. (For example, -1.0 will place the mask just to the left of the default mask position)

arguments.name: y
arguments.description: Shift by Y-axis measured in widths of the mask scaled to the face size, from left to right. (For example, -1.0 will place the mask just to the left of the default mask position)

arguments.name: zoom
arguments.description: Mask scaling coefficient. (For example, 2.0 means a doubled size)

parent.name: MaskCoords
parent.description: Mask coordinates (if this is a mask sticker, attached to a photo)
